<p class="ql-align-center">这周一年一度的万圣节要到啦～</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">为庆祝万圣节的来临</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">咱们小朋友会装扮成</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">各种可爱的鬼怪要糖果</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">否则就会捣蛋！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">Trick or treat！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那关于万圣节的英语小知识</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你知道吗？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>万圣节常用英语表达有哪些？</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">许多人将10月31日万圣节前夕称为万圣节</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但事实并非这样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">10月31日是万圣节前夜</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>英文：Halloween</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">11月1日才是万圣节</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>英文：Hallowmas 或 All Saints's Day</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201029/5926c48cf9a14f0eb36a5d8b4fbfaf79.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>万圣节常用词汇</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不给糖就捣蛋：<strong>trick or treat</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">糖果：<strong>candy/sweet</strong></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
