<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">南瓜：<strong>pumpkin</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一粒大南瓜：<strong>a big pumpkin</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">刻南瓜：<strong>carve the pumpkin</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">杰克灯（空心大南瓜）：<strong>jack-o-lanterns</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201029/2b7e9d211857443abcc76d260d00d423.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>万圣节装扮常用词汇</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">万圣节服装：<strong>Halloween costume</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">巫婆：<strong>witch</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">扫帚：<strong>broomstick</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鬼怪：<strong>monster/ghost</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">幽灵：<strong>ghost</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">咒语：<strong>curse</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">骨头：<strong>bone</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">骨头架：<strong>skeleton</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">面具：<strong>mask</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">蝙蝠：<strong>bat</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">蜘蛛网：<strong>spider web</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">十字架：<strong>the cross of jesus</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">死神：<strong>Grim Reaper</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">僵尸：<strong>zombie</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">吸血鬼：<strong>vampire</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201029/a5ded0e1786c4fcd9df50dbd44e18468.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>万圣节必备口语</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>1、You did give me a good scare!</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你着实吓了我一跳。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2、Do you want to help me make a jack-o’-lantern？</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你愿意帮我做个杰克灯/南瓜灯吗？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>3、Are you going to wear a mask？</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你要带面具吗？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>4、Let me give you some candies.</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我给你们些糖果吧~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>5、What are you going to be？</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你会打扮成什么？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>6、I am making my own costume.</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我要自己完成我的装扮。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201029/3bac3f82dbb04b88804abc3bfdb43dde.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>